    "body": "I did something similar to what you suggest, but definitely less elegant :-) \nI retrieved the objectID in this way \n\n```\nvar services_id = $.map(data.hits, function(o){\n                return o.objectID;\n }).join();\n\n```\n\nWhile we are in chat, could tell me how can I update an attribute of the algolia's indexed object?\n",
